snippet: Eugenie Bouchard of Canada needed only 52 minutes to beat Serbia’s Bojana Jovanovski, 6-1, 6-1, in the first round at the Connecticut Open.
abstract: Eugenie Bouchard beats Bojana Jovanovski in women's opening round at the Connecticut Open tennis tournament.
lead_paragraph: Eugenie Bouchard of Canada needed only 52 minutes to beat Serbia’s Bojana Jovanovski, 6-1, 6-1, in the first round at the Connecticut Open.
